Author: porcu93
Description: A set of challenging missions based around the Quadruple Decker bomb casing. Each bomb contains 47 of the same module. Requires the Quadruple Decker Bomb mod, the Multiple Bombs mod for the missions with at least 2 bombs and the Portal Room for missions with 3 and 4 bombs.
Name: Multiple Quadruple Decker Insanity
